summary:
Genuine HR professional, with a wealth of experience partnering with management to formulate and implement key HR strategies, business restructuring and change management to further organizational goals and create competitive advantage in demanding global environments. 

CORE COMPETENCIES
International Human Resource (HR) Management • Organizational Development •  Mergers & acquisitions  • Restructuring • Change Management • Organizational Alignment • Leadership Development • Succession Planning • Coaching & Mentoring • Employee Relations • Performance Management • Process Improvement • Multiculturalism • Employee Engagement • Recruitment & Retention • Strategic Analysis & Planning • Metrics Analysis • Development & Enforcement • Budgets & Cost Control • Compensation & Benefits • Employment Law/Regulatory • Compliance • Staff Development & Training •  Project Management • Team Building, Leadership & Motivation 
• Communication • Stakeholder Relationship Management • Negotiation & Conflict Resolution
